result.name: Gyukaku Japanese Yakiniku

reviews.text: affordable, great food, good service.

A very good Japanese Grill Restaurant located inside Windsor Building at Causeway.

Very easy to find at right after the escalator. 

You need to get a waiting list at the touch screen computer. 

You can also choose cooked food if you prefer not to grill. But i still suggest you to cook your own. It’s fan and you do it the way you like it.

Please the mushrooms and the oyster they are very very good.
Nice lunch and decent price . Around 300 for 2 person. Cheaper during week day
Excellent yakiniku. Must try at least once. Extensive menu. Reasonable prices. My mouth waters just thinking about it again. Recommended.
Good food and reasonable price.
